Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.84,0:00:19.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是闪闪发亮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.13,0:00:22.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  你在做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.26,0:00:24.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  阪本先生
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.14,0:00:27.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  不要去那边
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.21,0:00:31.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为阪本先生你最近脱毛得很厉害吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.40,0:00:34.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毛会粘在衣服上的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.46,0:00:39.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么啊小姑娘  你觉得我打扰到你了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.05,0:00:42.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要换衣服了  你稍微出去一下吧
Dialogue: 0,-0:00:00.50,-0:00:00.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.45,0:02:18.47,title-B,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(70,300)\fad(400,400)}日\N常\N之\N56
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.01,0:02:34.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阪本先生  你看  好适合我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.43,0:02:38.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那还不是因为这衣服是为小姑娘你量身定做的吗  这是当然的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.29,0:02:39.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.58,0:02:41.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛  这不是很适合吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.01,0:02:44.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是这样啦  不是这样啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.21,0:02:50.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看…看上去像普通的女孩子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.90,0:02:53.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛  看上去是和那边的小姑娘一样啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.43,0:02:56.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阪本先生  我喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.00,0:02:59.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阪本先生  最喜欢你了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.69,0:03:00.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  会沾上毛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.62,0:03:02.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙想干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.37,0:03:04.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是上学啦  上学
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.45,0:03:06.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许会交到朋友也说不定哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.95,0:03:08.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没有说过话呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.66,0:03:12.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  名乃  放学路上去吃冰激凌怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.18,0:03:15.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶  我去我去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.51,0:03:18.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么那之后去K歌吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.14,0:03:23.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶  但是我没有去过
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.61,0:03:26.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我教你唱  和大家一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.51,0:03:30.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  好  那么就…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.48,0:03:32.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这之类的事情哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.09,0:03:34.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好  名乃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.02,0:03:36.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  博士  早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.52,0:03:38.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你快看  博士
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.67,0:03:41.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样  适合我吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.40,0:03:44.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的…嗯  很帅气
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.89,0:03:47.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士～
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.92,0:03:51.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士你的也很合适哦  这件睡衣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.38,0:03:53.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈  帅气吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.25,0:03:55.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士很帅气！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.60,0:03:57.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不就和平时一样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.49,0:03:58.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阪本
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.20,0:04:00.40,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}你也这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.90,0:04:00.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阪本也很帅气
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.34,0:04:03.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手帕OK
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.45,0:04:04.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学生证OK
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.69,0:04:05.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教科书OK
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.90,0:04:06.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笔记本OK
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.85,0:04:07.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文具盒OK
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.03,0:04:09.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笔OK
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.20,0:04:10.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笔芯OK
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.12,0:04:14.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看看…好  没有忘带的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.68,0:04:16.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.75,0:04:18.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有忘带的东西哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.25,0:04:20.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶  是什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.56,0:04:22.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看看…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.29,0:04:22.64,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}肚子饿了的话呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.31,0:04:26.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就吃士力架！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.44,0:04:27.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.19,0:04:32.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厨房里准备了今天的早饭和午饭  要好好吃饭哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.94,0:04:39.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有洗好的衣服我回来再收  你不去管也没关系哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.61,0:04:42.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  学校大概几点放学啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.23,0:04:45.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概三点半吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.70,0:04:50.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为回来路上要去买晚饭的材料  到家大概是五点了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.45,0:04:52.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五点…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.63,0:04:55.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？  我没有说过吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.82,0:04:57.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五点就是晚上了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.98,0:05:00.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  但是因为要上学啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.80,0:05:01.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我就出门…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.00,0:05:04.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…博士？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.67,0:05:06.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然还是别去了！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.59,0:05:10.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶  你之前不是说去也没关系的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.11,0:05:11.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要走！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.52,0:05:14.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么这样  我要迟到了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.37,0:05:16.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请把书包还给我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.67,0:05:19.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的左手！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.42,0:05:24.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  小鬼  不要再这样不听话了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.27,0:05:28.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士…  那么就这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.22,0:05:31.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天晚上给博士做你喜欢吃的蛋包饭怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.16,0:05:36.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就…回家路上给你买鲨鱼蛋糕怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.55,0:05:42.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…那就  那就再追加一盒草莓果汁
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.34,0:05:46.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.01,0:05:47.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.23,0:05:49.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芥川奖也…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.98,0:05:52.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那我可没办法啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.12,0:05:54.85,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}蛋羹
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.07,0:05:57.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一时还真不知道怎么办了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.66,0:06:00.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之博士肯让步真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.14,0:06:04.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可是我作为普通人踏出的第一步
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.79,0:06:13.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了  我全忘光了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.23,0:06:16.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,背上的发条要怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,-0:00:00.30,-0:00:00.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.13,0:06:22.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帅到掉渣的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.32,0:06:32.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.12,0:06:35.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦！  变得有干劲的学姐！
Dialogue: 0,-0:00:00.30,-0:00:00.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.93,0:06:37.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.65,0:06:41.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论怎么想  都没有能够解答的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.28,0:06:43.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果还是走到这儿来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.34,0:06:46.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来向大家介绍转校生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.60,0:06:47.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,东云同学
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.15,0:06:48.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.71,0:07:05.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果…果然大家很在意发条
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.35,0:07:09.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来  东云同学  请写自己的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.13,0:07:14.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发条太显眼了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.83,0:07:16.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是不想个办法混过去的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.84,0:07:20.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我…我叫东云名乃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.64,0:07:23.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那个  是这么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.31,0:07:25.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  这个发条是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.62,0:07:27.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…那什么…实际上是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.79,0:07:29.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在路上刺进去的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.76,0:07:33.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了  大家反而更在意了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.08,0:07:35.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶  不…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.57,0:07:38.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那个…总之  实际上是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.68,0:07:40.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我瞎说的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.93,0:07:44.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了  我为什么要改口啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.05,0:07:46.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.85,0:07:48.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…那个
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.52,0:07:50.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…我是说
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.57,0:07:55.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使转动大拇趾  也不会发现里面有USB这种机器人般的东西…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.38,0:07:57.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经撑不下去了
Dialogue: 0,-0:00:00.30,-0:00:00.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.30,0:08:03.36,title-B,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(280,260)\fad(400,400)}占\N卜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.67,0:08:06.90,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}「あした天気になあれ」一种儿童游戏，踢出鞋子来占卜天气\N和穿着的时候一样就是晴，翻过来是雨，鞋子横过来是阴。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.67,0:08:06.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天会是好天气～
Dialogue: 0,-0:00:00.30,-0:00:00.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.15,0:08:13.70,title-B,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,300)\fad(400,400)}日\N常\N之\N57
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.18,0:08:13.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说关口
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.95,0:08:15.69,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}围棋足球部
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.31,0:08:15.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要老是看书啦  来玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.45,0:08:19.82,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}日本类似大富翁的桌面游戏，加入了各种人生经历。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.45,0:08:19.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难得我买了人生游戏来玩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.65,0:08:19.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(190,93)\fs20\fad(600,0)}围棋足球部  部长
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.50,0:08:22.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(520,93)\fs20\fad(600,0)}围棋足球部  部员
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.26,0:08:26.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  好闲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.43,0:08:29.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然我们是围棋足球部  就来解棋局吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.44,0:08:30.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我不会围棋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.02,0:08:33.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.84,0:08:38.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  这里是围棋足球部吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.75,0:08:39.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.84,0:08:41.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想要入部
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.20,0:08:47.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超级欢迎啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.66,0:08:48.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你叫什么名字
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.17,0:08:51.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一…一年级的樱井诚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.98,0:08:55.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  我是二年级的部长大工健三郎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.34,0:08:57.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这位是一年级的关口同学
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.35,0:09:00.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛嘛  赶快坐下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.05,0:09:01.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.23,0:09:03.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  要玩什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.12,0:09:05.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玩人生游戏吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.07,0:09:08.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那什么  不练习一下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.21,0:09:11.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,围棋足球的练习
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.08,0:09:17.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实际上围棋足球只是我创造的传说中的社团罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.96,0:09:19.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实并没有那种竞技运动
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.84,0:09:22.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基本上只是大家在一起玩就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.99,0:09:25.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛  说起来就是娱乐部罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.59,0:09:31.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我初中的时候就在围棋足球部
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.04,0:09:36.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还不知道这学校里有围棋足球部呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.77,0:09:41.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是因为前阵子在校舍前看到条幅才注意到的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.05,0:09:45.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实际上我在初中的时候是MVP
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.13,0:09:48.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶…诶…
Dialogue: 0,-0:00:00.30,-0:00:00.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.71,0:09:57.95,title-B,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(620,250)\fad(400,400)}在\N意
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.90,0:10:00.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,东…东云同学
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.54,0:10:01.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.82,0:10:05.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那个  无论如何我都很在意
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.53,0:10:07.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那背上的…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.30,0:10:11.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.39,0:10:13.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  那个
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.69,0:10:14.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个
Dialogue: 0,-0:00:00.30,-0:00:00.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.17,0:10:17.70,title-B,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(240,300)\fad(400,400)}日\N常\N之\N57.5
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.64,0:10:18.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  围棋足球部都在做些什么样的活动呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.52,0:10:23.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  用语言来说明好像很难呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.30,0:10:25.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我就来个自我示范好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.89,0:10:28.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先是颠球
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.73,0:10:31.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,颠球之后是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.27,0:10:33.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,棋子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.59,0:10:41.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后是棋子之后的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.29,0:10:44.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,德意志后背摔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.02,0:10:49.29,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}「ナダレ定石」某种围棋的着法。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.02,0:10:49.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是崩坏式着法三连星！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.17,0:10:54.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.37,0:10:58.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来是以随便的心情创立这个社团的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.35,0:10:59.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.88,0:11:02.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像变得有趣起来了
Dialogue: 0,-0:00:00.30,-0:00:00.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.39,0:11:05.64,title-B,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(100,260)\fad(400,400)}鞋\N子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.03,0:11:22.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下啦  你突然是怎么了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.33,0:11:24.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要去哪里啊  伙伴
Dialogue: 0,-0:00:00.30,-0:00:00.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.33,0:11:29.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(00,00)}一句话时间
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.45,0:11:36.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阪本
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.37,0:11:39.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阪本阪本阪本阪本…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.24,0:11:38.63,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}喂  等…  不要这样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.04,0:11:42.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若问「这是怎么回事」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.75,0:11:44.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是咕噜咕噜地转
Dialogue: 0,-0:00:00.30,-0:00:00.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.90,0:11:55.45,title-B,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(90,270)\fad(400,400)\bord10\shad0\be30\3a&H50\3c&HFFFFFF&}伙\N\N伴
Dialogue: 0,-0:00:00.20,-0:00:00.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.80,0:12:21.79,title-B,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(600,300)\fad(400,400)}日\N常\N之\N58
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.47,0:12:29.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一天就这么失败
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.26,0:12:33.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家会不会怀疑我是个怪孩子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.32,0:12:35.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶  名乃带了便当啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.49,0:12:38.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.23,0:12:39.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看上去很好吃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.01,0:12:41.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平常也是吃便当吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.63,0:12:42.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.74,0:12:45.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很普通的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.21,0:12:53.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给你看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.11,0:13:00.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很帅气…呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.25,0:13:06.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美绪久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.27,0:13:09.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好慢啊祐子  午休都快结束了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.03,0:13:11.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.29,0:13:14.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀  我回来的时候  鞋子被车子和狗带走了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.87,0:13:16.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜其所赐我真是糟透了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.66,0:13:19.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然总觉得不知道事情的具体展开
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.93,0:13:21.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之好像是很了不得的事情呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.44,0:13:25.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛  但是平安送到真是最好不过了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.85,0:13:28.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？  祐子的午饭呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.75,0:13:30.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一边走就一边吃掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.69,0:13:32.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶  你吃了什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.46,0:13:33.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回锅肉便当
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.12,0:13:34.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好强…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.99,0:13:36.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回锅…是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.74,0:13:37.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛  算了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.17,0:13:41.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  名乃  和我们一起吃怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.08,0:13:45.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告诉我们名乃的各种事情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.58,0:13:47.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.02,0:13:51.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会不会认为我是个普通的孩子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.69,0:13:54.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫…莫非会成为朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.06,0:13:56.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  名乃背上的那个东西
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.76,0:14:01.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这绝对不是什么奇怪的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.00,0:14:04.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道名乃是机器人？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.27,0:14:09.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  你在说什么蠢话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.59,0:14:11.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  祐子她是笨蛋啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.20,0:14:14.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  已经没有时间了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.22,0:14:17.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名乃抱歉  今天就快速解决吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.55,0:14:21.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.73,0:14:39.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  祐子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.78,0:14:40.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.26,0:14:42.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是烤青花鱼哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.31,0:14:46.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我拜托你买的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.07,0:14:49.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？  不是烤青花鱼吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.03,0:14:50.63,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}烤青花鱼「焼きさば」和炒面「焼きそば」一字之差。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.03,0:14:50.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是炒面啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.70,0:14:55.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  莫非是我听错了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.12,0:14:56.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歉抱歉抱歉抱
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.00,0:14:59.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是那种装天然呆的问题啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.26,0:15:00.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是很严重的问题啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.88,0:15:02.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是很相似吗  
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.24,0:15:04.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为只差了一个假名啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.23,0:15:05.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不能因为这就…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.84,0:15:10.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个就算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.97,0:15:12.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么饭在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.92,0:15:14.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.86,0:15:16.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白米饭啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.56,0:15:18.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…我只买了那个
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.07,0:15:21.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有鱼你要我怎么吃啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.05,0:15:24.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是  因为美绪你只说了烤青花鱼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.92,0:15:26.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是说的炒面啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.63,0:15:29.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是炒过的面啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.21,0:15:30.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.35,0:15:35.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你看  这样的事情可以当做素材写到博客上嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.88,0:15:37.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没有电脑啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.43,0:15:41.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  即使你这样生气也…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.30,0:15:45.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了啦  我现在再去买  给我钱
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.61,0:15:48.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么我要再给你一次钱啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.68,0:15:50.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我没钱了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.34,0:15:52.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 算了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.69,0:15:54.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了  你赶快买来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.03,0:15:56.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,午休要结束了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.76,0:15:58.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK  OK
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.21,0:16:03.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.97,0:16:05.40,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}第六话出现的西班牙古币，中南美等国货币单位。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.97,0:16:05.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只有比索了啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.62,0:16:07.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只有这个之前作为纪念而留下的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.77,0:16:09.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿根廷比索了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.66,0:16:13.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只有阿根廷比索了啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.36,0:16:15.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿根廷比索
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.08,0:16:16.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是因为祐子你听错了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.94,0:16:18.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以钱应该由你来付啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.43,0:16:21.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都说了我买了自己的便当  钱都花光了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.49,0:16:23.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我的午饭要怎么办啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.80,0:16:28.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那就  于是就吃青花鱼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.37,0:16:30.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,青花鱼啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.63,0:16:31.40,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}青花鱼？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.29,0:16:33.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  我以前开始就看你不爽了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.75,0:16:36.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每次每次都抄人家的作业
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.15,0:16:38.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少自己稍微做一下会死啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.62,0:16:39.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这笨蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.87,0:16:45.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是笨蛋这一点和美绪你吃不到午饭完全没有关系吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.43,0:16:46.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全有关系啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.94,0:16:48.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么  你说说看啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.40,0:16:50.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为是笨蛋才会听错的啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.55,0:16:55.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说只是听错而已  谁都会犯这样的错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.56,0:16:58.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老是纠缠不休的  你心胸太狭窄了啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.16,0:17:01.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我本来就没吃早饭  这可是生死攸关的问题啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.36,0:17:03.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正笨蛋是不会懂的啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.48,0:17:04.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不是笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.59,0:17:06.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才你自己认同自己是笨蛋了对吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.62,0:17:10.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我话说在前面  下次我绝对不会给祐子作业抄了！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.30,0:17:11.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊  很好很好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.95,0:17:15.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美绪你忘记作业的话我也不会给你抄的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.07,0:17:17.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁要看你那糟糕的作业啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.78,0:17:21.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说到底是你买错了  至少也给我道个歉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.18,0:17:23.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你给我跪下啦  跪下！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.72,0:17:26.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是是是是  只要跪就好了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.97,0:17:27.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就跪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.10,0:17:30.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  真的是…非常抱歉啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.07,0:17:32.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看吧  我道歉了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.30,0:17:34.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就行了吧  这样！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.21,0:17:36.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈？  你那不是下跪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.78,0:17:39.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是啊  确实不是下跪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.05,0:17:41.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是前屈啦  前屈
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.80,0:17:43.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么不下跪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.94,0:17:48.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我受够了啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.81,0:17:51.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说美绪你才是笨蛋吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.83,0:17:54.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前那个奇怪的插画算什么啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.44,0:17:57.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…奇怪的插画
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.78,0:17:59.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你是白痴吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.11,0:18:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.01,0:18:03.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么插画啊  不知所云啦  不知所云
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.23,0:18:05.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个淫荡的样子  还戴眼镜呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.67,0:18:06.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是白痴吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.21,0:18:09.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是白痴吗  你是白痴吗  你是白痴吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.90,0:18:10.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说啥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.74,0:18:13.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,画那种白痴插画的你才是白痴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.52,0:18:14.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.80,0:18:17.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来  赶快吃掉啊  你拜托我买的烤青花鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.01,0:18:19.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是炒面才对吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.62,0:18:22.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我下跪道歉  头要深深地埋下去！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.99,0:18:25.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我买都买来了  已经没办法了不是！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.20,0:18:26.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像个人样好好道歉啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.50,0:18:27.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这人渣啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.32,0:18:29.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.44,0:18:32.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就让你看看真正的下跪！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.04,0:18:34.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这才是真正的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.92,0:18:38.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下跪啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.09,0:18:42.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「买了烤青花鱼真是对不起」的道歉呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.62,0:18:44.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下跪了就要好好谢罪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.57,0:18:47.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快给我说啊  「买了烤青花鱼真是对不起」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.99,0:18:52.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么就快点说啊  「我是笨蛋真是对不起」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.22,0:18:54.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要从心底给我道歉  你这人渣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.60,0:18:56.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来啊  快说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.03,0:18:57.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快张口给我说啊  笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.73,0:18:59.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点道歉  呆子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.39,0:19:01.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人渣  白痴  笨蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.53,0:19:03.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看我的！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.66,0:19:18.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  老是笨蛋笨蛋的  吵死了啦  美绪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.26,0:19:21.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不过跟我相处了半年  你以为你有多了解我啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.86,0:19:24.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你才是  你以为你有多了解我的画啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.04,0:19:29.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道啊  你若是画得那么好  干嘛不去当个漫画家啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.28,0:19:36.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你在说什么啊  你是笨蛋吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.16,0:19:38.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈？  说别人是笨蛋的人才是笨蛋吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.91,0:19:40.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.17,0:19:41.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你自己不也说我笨蛋吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.89,0:19:42.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才没说啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.23,0:19:44.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.12,0:19:48.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我不讨厌你那一点
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.22,0:19:54.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈？  你在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.79,0:19:55.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明很聪明
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.91,0:20:00.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵…吵死了啦  你这微笑的天才
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.22,0:20:04.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…什么啊  你才是  明明画画得那么好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.19,0:20:05.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了  你明明跑得那么快
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.92,0:20:07.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你明明很聪明
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.15,0:20:08.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你明明那么乐天派
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.43,0:20:09.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你明明很聪明
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.84,0:20:11.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你才是  你明明很聪明
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.36,0:20:28.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害
