Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.63,0:20:43.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前辈  我好不甘心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.95,0:20:46.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别哭了  你们还有明年
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.64,0:20:48.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要连前辈的份一起努力
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.12,0:20:51.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.33,0:20:55.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是过去的事情了
Dialogue: 0,-0:00:00.20,-0:00:00.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.77,0:21:02.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂  名乃  学校好玩吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.39,0:21:03.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.17,0:21:05.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实发生了各种事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.28,0:21:07.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.43,0:21:08.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么说？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.52,0:21:09.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么说？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.85,0:21:13.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋友的力量真是太强大了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.87,0:21:15.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那真是强大
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.04,0:21:18.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂  搞不懂你们在说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.83,0:21:21.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.67,0:21:28.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.40,0:21:28.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.96,0:21:31.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请帮我取下背上的发条
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.61,0:21:33.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.48,0:21:35.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为…为什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.12,0:21:38.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会给学校生活带来各种障碍的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.77,0:21:41.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天都被别人怀疑是机器人了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.04,0:21:44.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去就交不到朋友了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.65,0:21:46.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交得到哦  因为很可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.72,0:21:48.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.28,0:21:49.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很可爱哦  发条
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.94,0:21:51.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了啦  赶快做饭啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.93,0:21:53.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士
Dialogue: 0,-0:00:00.20,-0:00:00.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.76,0:23:27.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是足球
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.52,0:23:29.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,踢呀踢呀被踢了个遍呀
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.57,0:23:32.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,踢到坏掉  踢到死掉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.34,0:23:34.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后我就长眠了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.72,0:23:39.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回的日常是第十五话  敬请期待
