Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.92,0:01:03.15,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}那就把你玩个够
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.74,0:01:01.30,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)\an6}S\Nh\Ni\Nn\Ne\N!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.02,0:01:05.53,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.12,0:01:04.90,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}Lan Lan Lan
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.53,0:01:07.15,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}真高兴啊  简直爽的没边儿
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.21,0:01:10.53,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}有什么不愉快的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.05,0:01:08.35,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)\an6}W\Nh\Ny
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.65,0:01:12.91,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}马上就抛到脑后
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.42,0:01:11.00,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)\an6}F\Ni\Nn\Ne
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.44,0:01:15.16,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}不管什么时候
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.99,0:01:14.37,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}Lan Lan Lan
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.22,0:01:16.83,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}都全力以赴
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.14,0:01:19.54,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}24小时在一起也没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.66,0:01:21.93,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}就像双生子亲子或者克隆细胞
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.03,0:01:24.25,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}那就完全没有必要恋爱了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.39,0:01:27.12,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}那个和这个完全完全没关系啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.48,0:01:29.71,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}吵架的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.24,0:01:27.79,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)\an6}F\Ni\Ng\Nh\Nt
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.83,0:01:31.96,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}心情很不好的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.69,0:01:30.32,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)\an6}D\No\Nw\Nn\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.18,0:01:34.38,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}想要独处的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.88,0:01:32.66,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)\an6}S\Nh\No\Nc\Nk
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.50,0:01:39.25,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}忽然发现你们就在身边  要死一起死
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.22,0:01:42.37,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}为什么呢  只想在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.49,0:01:45.10,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}与你在一起  时间过得飞快
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.22,0:01:47.14,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}真高兴  实在太高兴了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.26,0:01:48.52,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}不愧是最好的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.67,0:01:49.89,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}怎怎怎怎怎怎怎怎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.99,0:01:52.05,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}怎么回事啊  这高到异常的同步率
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.15,0:01:54.69,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}总是吵吵闹闹  给邻居带来不少烦恼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.79,0:01:56.82,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}现在几点了  一会儿去吃个够
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.92,0:01:58.01,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}完全不明白怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.17,0:02:00.62,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}那·又·怎·么·样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.74,0:02:01.78,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}比想象中好得多
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.90,0:02:03.05,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}怎么说呢  就是最棒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.15,0:02:04.26,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}再·怎·么·说  咱们都是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.36,0:02:05.46,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}好朋友  嘿哟
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.56,0:02:06.62,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}极上  友情
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.79,0:02:08.01,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}事事都要顺利
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.35,0:02:11.87,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}锵啦锵  锵啦锵…锵
