Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.32,0:22:25.65,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}翼がほしい
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.86,0:22:29.87,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}この背中に
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.65,0:22:35.01,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}鳥のように
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.72,0:22:48.06,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}白い翼つけてください
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.47,0:22:53.53,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}この大空に翼をひろげ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.61,0:22:58.42,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}飛んで行きたいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.69,0:23:03.82,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}悲しみのない自由な空へ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.89,0:23:08.65,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}翼はためかせ
